{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"TransformStreamDefaultController.desiredSize","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TransformStreamDefaultController/desiredSize","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TransformStreamDefaultController\"><code>TransformStreamDefaultController</code></a> 接口的只读属性 <strong><code>desiredSize</code></strong> 返回填充满关联的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ReadableStream\"><code>ReadableStream</code></a> 的内部队列所需要的大小。</p>\n<p><code>ReadableStream</code> 的内部队列包含已入队但尚未读取的分块。浏览器确定填满流<strong>所需要的大小</strong>，并且这个值由 <code>desiredSize</code> 属性返回。</p>\n<p>如果这个 <code>desiredSize</code> 是 <code>0</code>，则队列已满。因此你可以使用这个信息去<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Streams_API/Concepts#backpressure\">手动管理背压</a>去管理队列。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"值","title":"值","isH3":false,"content":"<p>所需的大小。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>在下面的示例中，<code>desiredSize</code> 被打印到控制台。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>controller<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>desiredSize<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://streams.spec.whatwg.org/#ts-default-controller-desired-size","title":"Streams Standard"}],"query":"api.TransformStreamDefaultController.desiredSize"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.TransformStreamDefaultController.desiredSize","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TransformStreamDefaultController/desiredSize/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"值